{"tid":1743242,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天水圍頭中催淚彈孤兒仍危殆 網民集氣支持","createTime":"2019-11-21T06:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:52:43.000Z","uid":209307,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"22a58d9e61dbd35cab69b8e814fa9770dd6dd153","tid":1743242,"uid":209307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:18:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Source: <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60291858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60291858&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameAUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=b0090151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191121%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60291858&h=7d362de6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191121&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60291858</a><br />\n<br />\n15歲少年傅同學11月13日晚在天水圍被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部重創，即晚入院進行開腦手術後，情況未見好轉。傅同學父母雙亡，與兄長雙依為命並由叔父照顧，今日再有網上消息傳出，傅同學病情仍然未見好轉，求網民集氣支持；協助傅同學的基督教信義會青少年服務總監竺永洪向《蘋果》表示，傅同學仍然危殆，手術後一直於深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，11月13日晚上約9時，逾百巿民包圍天水圍警署，並在附近街道設路障及磚頭陣，期間向警署投擲汽油彈，警署停車場一度火光熊熊。警方其後在警署高層向外發射催淚彈，短時間內發射至少50枚，未幾防暴警衝出向人群發射催淚彈驅散；至晚上10時許，傅同學在天水圍新北江商場對開，被防暴警發射的催淚彈擊中頭部昏迷，義務救護員進行急救再送院。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">千祈唔好有事，求大家集氣！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"159e345c5e37afc317b1f1112245ba363214baf0","tid":1743242,"uid":138740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲時候好唔想正皮.."},{"pid":"f56e1afd34c8ea6cce26bc021e7addf85d55bcfd","tid":1743242,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"手足頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b4d0ebcd0b4549c007ce8b904d541ac7ea41d2","tid":1743242,"uid":209307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"手足頂住！！"},{"pid":"21ccce647c81cef3835a117751aa227a38cdbe04","tid":1743242,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"仲係危殆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca45baf4d4026610c24da0fa1ea81e8bbd46c978","tid":1743242,"uid":141219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"Add oil bro"},{"pid":"997c66751e91ff52b5a0bc4c85b3fc3bc3b38db8","tid":1743242,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdf5dd7af78eabc006ef0b99da6e4f26ac1403b","tid":1743242,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ea1faaf9f132ea37561e402fcf75c5dbe5a868","tid":1743242,"uid":248105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:28:12.000Z","msg":"集氣"},{"pid":"d9e9b280227dca7da632b1c7d9251771732fbdce","tid":1743242,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"死黑警又殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34